########## actor_in ##########


The l Isa location
  
End The l.

The cont Isa object
  At l 
  With Container
End The cont.
Syntax
  enter = 'enter' (cont)
    Where cont Isa container
      Else 
        "You can only enter containers."
  

Verb enter
  Does
    If hero In cont Then
      "You are already inside the $1."
    Else 
      Locate hero In cont.
    End If.
End Verb.


